  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study hypothesis: Valsartan as an angiotensin II receptor blocker treatment has
      beneficial effects on both midwall mechanics and myocardial functions in hypertensive
      patients with Left ventricular hypertrophy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
